1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">jettison,</tr_> Syngr. ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg035.perseus-grc1:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">35.11</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n31709.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cast out of</tr_> a place, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Κιμμερίους ἐκβαλόντες ἐκ τῆς Εὐρώπης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.103</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐ. ἐκ τῆς χώρας,</foreign> of an enemy, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0034.tlg001.perseus-grc1:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Lycurg.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">99</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg060.perseus-grc1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">60.8</biblScope> </bibl> ; esp. of banishment, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκ πόλεως ἐ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drive out of</tr_> the country, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg023:468d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Grg.\">Grg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">468d</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg011.perseus-grc1:430\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl